## 5. .env.example

```env
# Supabase
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://tu-proyecto.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=tu-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=tu-service-key

# Cloudflare R2
R2_ENDPOINT=https://tu-account-id.r2.cloudflarestorage.com
R2_ACCESS_KEY=tu-access-key
R2_SECRET_KEY=tu-secret-key
R2_BUCKET=procivil-documents

# Email Service (Resend)
RESEND_API_KEY=tu-resend-api-key
FROM_EMAIL=alertas@procivil.com

# Microservice
MICROSERVICE_URL=https://tu-microservice.railway.app
JWT_SECRET=tu-jwt-secret

# Monitoring
SENTRY_DSN=tu-sentry-dsn

# Production URLs
FRONTEND_URL=https://tu-app.vercel.app
API_URL=https://tu-proyecto.supabase.co/rest/v1